ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.v28.group

Class OPU_R25_ORDER

  • java.lang.Object
    • ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.AbstractStructure
      • ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.AbstractGroup
        • ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.v28.group.OPU_R25_ORDER
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Group, Structure, Visitable, Serializable

    public class OPU_R25_ORDER
extends AbstractGroup

    Represents a OPU_R25_ORDER group structure (a Group object). A Group is an ordered collection of message segments that can repeat together or be optionally in/excluded together. This Group contains the following elements:

    • 1: OBR (Observation Request)
    • 2: PRT (Participation Information) optional repeating
    • 3: OPU_R25_COMMON_ORDER (a Group object) optional
    • 4: NTE (Notes and Comments) optional repeating
    • 5: PRT (Participation Information) optional repeating
    • 6: OPU_R25_TIMING_QTY (a Group object) optional repeating
    • 7: OPU_R25_RESULT (a Group object) repeating
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
